<lyrics>[V1]
 Jesuh min kha thangthat ko u, Vanmi nih thangthat fawn; Vanmi nih
 thangthat fawn, Sunparnak kha va pe u law.

[C1]
   Chinhter u si, Chinhter u si, Chinhter u si, lianngan Khamhtu Bawi
   bik cu. Chinhter u si,chinhter u si Chinhter u si,Bawi bik cu.

[V2]
 Bawi Jesuh ca a thimi hna, Amah thangthatnak in, Amah thangthatnak in,
 Kan Khamhbawi ca hlasa u si.

[C2]
   Chinhter u si, Chinhter u si, Chinhter u si, lianngan Khamhtu Bawi
   bik cu. Chinhter u si,chinhter u si Chinhter u si,Bawi bik cu.

[V3]
 Jen-tail mi nih philh hin hlah u, Nan ca Khamhbawi innak; Nan ca
 Khamhbawi innak, Amah sinah laksawng pe u.

[C3]
   Chinhter u si, Chinhter u si, Chinhter u si, lianngan Khamhtu Bawi
   bik cu. Chinhter u si,chinhter u si Chinhter u si,Bawi bik cu.

[V4]
 Vawlei miphun zakip vialte, Jesuh hlorh cio ko u, Jesuh hlorh cio ko
 u, A lianngan bik Bawi si ko seh, (Bawi bik cu, Bawi bik cu chinhter u,
 Bawi bik cu chinhter u).

[C4]
   Chinhter u si, Chinhter u si, Chinhter u si, lianngan Khamhtu Bawi
   bik cu. Chinhter u si,chinhter u si Chinhter u si,Bawi bik cu.

[V5]
 Vancung mithiang mi hna he khin, Amah cu kan biak lai, Amah cu kan
 biak lai, A zungzal hla kan sa ti lai, (Bawi bik cu, Bawi bik cu chinhter
 u, Bawi bik cu chinhter u).

[C5]
   Chinhter u si, Chinhter u si, Chinhter u si, lianngan Khamhtu Bawi
   bik cu. Chinhter u si,chinhter u si Chinhter u si,Bawi bik cu.</lyrics>
<title>CHINHTER U SI CH149</title>
<hymn_number>149</hymn_number>
</song>